back\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 12, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mwg1665703141361.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mwg1665703141361.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mwg1665703141361.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mwg1665703141361\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"mwg1665703141361__uniface_dspinstance_414336\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.DSPInstance</span> object provides access to selected properties of the DSP component instance that it represents. Deprecated.\n   </p>\n<div class=\"note important note_important\" id=\"mwg1665703141361__note_w533ab1b5b1_w534ab1b5_w535ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Important:</span> The object\n            <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.DSPInstance</span> is deprecated. Use\n            <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span> instead. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dtg1665702533539.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dtg1665702533539.html\" title=\"The uniface.Instance object provides access to selected properties and methods of the component instance that it represents.\">uniface.Instance</a>.</div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mwg1665703141361__topic_d88697e1_d88698e1_d88699e1_d88700e1_d88701e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d385006e71\">\n                       \n Functions\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Data Addressing Functions</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Function</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lrj1665702533649.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrj1665702533649.html\" title=\"Returns the fully qualified name of the current Uniface JavaScript object.\">getName()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1__entry__2\">Returns the name of the\n                           <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qlx1665702533740.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qlx1665702533740.html\" title=\"Returns the unqualified name of the current Uniface JavaScript object.\">getShortName()</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1__entry__2\">Returns the short name of the current\n                           <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span>. For a <code class=\"ph codeph\">DSPInstance</code>,\n                        this is the same as its name. However, other API objects have a similar\n                        function that returns shorter names than <code class=\"ph codeph\">getName</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"agg1665702533827.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/agg1665702533827.html\" title=\"Returns a constant string denoting the object type.\">getType()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1__entry__2\">\n Returns a constant string denoting the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span> type: <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.TYPE_DSPINSTANCE</span>.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"udv1665702533913.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/udv1665702533913.html\" title=\"Returns an Uniface JavaScript object that represents the parent of the current object.\">getParent()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1__entry__2\">Returns <code class=\"ph codeph\">null</code> because a\n                           <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span> is always a top-level object. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pic1665702532756.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pic1665702532756.html\" title=\"Returns the component name of this component instance, or the main component instance.\">getComponentName()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1__entry__2\">\n Returns the component name of this <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span>.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gtd1665702532835.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gtd1665702532835.html\" title=\"Returns an array of uniface.Entity objects contained by the current object, or by the main instance.\">getEntities()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1__entry__2\">\n Returns an array of <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Entity</span> objects representing the outer entities of the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span>.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oel1665702532918.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oel1665702532918.html\" title=\"Get the named entity in the specified occurrence or component instance, or the main instance.\">getEntity()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1__entry__2\">\n Returns the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Entity</span> object that represents the named outer entity.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dlv1665702534001.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dlv1665702534001.html\" title=\"Indicates whether the current Uniface JavaScript object equals another JavaScript object, meaning that they both represent the same Uniface object.\">isEqualTo()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15104e1_d15105e1_d15106e1__entry__2\">\n Checks whether the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span> object is the same as another <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.getInstance</span> object.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15107e1_d15108e1_d15109e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Invocation API Functions</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15107e1_d15108e1_d15109e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Function</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15107e1_d15108e1_d15109e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15107e1_d15108e1_d15109e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tle1665702533236.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tle1665702533236.html\" title=\"Asynchronously activates an operation on the current component instance, or the main instance.\">activate()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15107e1_d15108e1_d15109e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Activate an operation or supported trigger on the current DSP instance.\n                           The called operation can be executed on the client or the server,\n                           depending on how it is declared.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15107e1_d15108e1_d15109e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lnp1665702533422.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lnp1665702533422.html\" title=\"Removes a component instance from memory.\">remove</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwg1665703141361__table_d15107e1_d15108e1_d15109e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Detach and delete the current DSP instance, detaching any child\n                           instances.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mwg1665703141361__topic_d88702e1_d88703e1_d88704e1_d88705e1_d88706e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d385006e363\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mwg1665703141361__p_d125843e1_d125844e1_d125845e1\">The <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span> object is returned by the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.getInstance</span> function. The <span class=\"keyword apiname\">getParent</span> function of a <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Entity</span> object can also return a <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span> object.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xmp1665702533078.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getInstance()</a><p>Returns a reference to the uniface.Instance object that represents a given DSP instance name on the browser.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jwv1665702534619.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getInstance()</a><p>Returns a reference to the uniface.Instance object that contains the current object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/udv1665702533913.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getParent()</a><p>Returns an Uniface JavaScript object that represents the parent of the current object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/osn1665702667912.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>DSP Component Instances</a><p>DSP component instances differ from those of other components in that they are split—a non-persistent part runs on the server, and a persistent part runs on the browser. Communication between the two parts is asynchronous, via HTTP requests and responses over the internet. Uniface automatically handles communication and synchronization.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530114\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530114\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "uniface.DSPInstance Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 12, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The uniface.DSPInstance object provides access to selected properties of the DSP component instance that it represents. Deprecated. Important: The object uniface.DSPInstance is deprecated. Use uniface.Instance instead. For more information, see uniface.Instance . Functions Table 1. Data Addressing Functions Function Description getName() Returns the name of the uniface.Instance . getShortName() Returns the short name of the current uniface.Instance . For a DSPInstance , this is the same as its name. However, other API objects have a similar function that returns shorter names than getName . getType() Returns a constant string denoting the uniface.Instance type: uniface.TYPE_DSPINSTANCE . getParent() Returns null because a uniface.Instance is always a top-level object. getComponentName() Returns the component name of this uniface.Instance . getEntities() Returns an array of uniface.Entity objects representing the outer entities of the uniface.Instance . getEntity() Returns the uniface.Entity object that represents the named outer entity. isEqualTo() Checks whether the uniface.Instance object is the same as another uniface.getInstance object. Table 2. Invocation API Functions Function Description activate() Activate an operation or supported trigger on the current DSP instance. The called operation can be executed on the client or the server, depending on how it is declared. remove Detach and delete the current DSP instance, detaching any child instances. Description The uniface.Instance object is returned by the uniface.getInstance function. The getParent function of a uniface.Entity object can also return a uniface.Instance object. Related Links getInstance() Returns a reference to the uniface.Instance object that represents a given DSP instance name on the browser. getInstance() Returns a reference to the uniface.Instance object that contains the current object. getParent() Returns an Uniface JavaScript object that represents the parent of the current object. DSP Component Instances DSP component instances differ from those of other components in that they are split—a non-persistent part runs on the server, and a persistent part runs on the browser. Communication between the two parts is asynchronous, via HTTP requests and responses over the internet. Uniface automatically handles communication and synchronization. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}